The overly popular HTML templating language PHP. Have a look at http://ios-webstack.tk .
 The overly popular HTML templating language PHP.

 This packages includes PHP 5.5.x with GD and MySQL support (PDO and mysqli).

 This software was originally compiled for the AppleTV but it works on all iOS devices.

 You have to place your PHP config file at /etc/php.ini

 With the additional cydia packages 'mysql-atv' and 'lighttpd-atv' you are now free to host your own Content Management Systems (CMS), Blogs, Bulletin Boards, File Servers.
 Such as ownCloud, WebsiteBaker, Contao, TYPO3, WordPress, Joomla!, phpBB, miniBB, etc.

 If you would like keep it simple then just install one of the AwkwardTV/BigBoss packages below:
 - 'atv-lighttpd-php-mysql' for AppleTV
 - 'ios-lighttpd-php-mysql' for iPhone/iPad
 - 'touch-lighttpd-php-mysql' for iPhone/iPad

 They includes this, the above mentioned packages, example config files and daemon launchers for a whole web server solution stack.

 If you are interest in the package differences, have a look on http://ios-webstack.tk . 
